{"word":"G649 - ἀποστέλλω - apostéllō - ap-os-tel'-lo - Put in","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποστέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apostéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-os-tel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Put in</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனுப்பு, அனுப்பிவிடு, துரத்திவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to send off, send away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G4724 - στέλλω - stéllō - stel'-lo/4724\">G4724</a>; <i>set apart</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>send out</i> (properly on a mission) literally or figuratively: - put in, send (away, forth, out), set [at liberty].</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1821/1821\">G1821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3992/3992\">G3992</a>, <a href=\"#/G5570/5570\">G5570</a>, <a href=\"#/G649/649\">G649</a>, <a href=\"#/G651/651\">G651</a>, <a href=\"#/G652/652\">G652</a>"}]}